About me

My name is Vijay Sharma, and I am a highly skilled and creative interior designer with a passion for transforming spaces into functional and aesthetically pleasing environments. As a graduate of the Artemisia College of Art & Design (ACAD), I’m passionate about finding the true potential of each and every space.

This portfolio is a testament to my commitment to excellence and attention to detail. I am excited to share my work with you and look forward to the opportunity to bring my expertise and creativity to your next project.
